2 Sons of Genius. 3[superscript]d[/superscript] To St [superscript]t[/superscript] Michaels
There were the visions of my youth
That fled before there was a [unclear]xxxxxx[/unclear]
Sat [unclear]Thoera[/unclear] the fair with Henry the good
Ah stay a little longer give thy light
To man the Child of sorrow and of care
In radiant hope illumes the scene
